    main.content
      section.description.page__description.section.page__section(
        aria-label="Block with an article"
      )
        .container.page__container
          article.article.description__article
            h2.article__title.title
              | The main problems in learning
            .article__main-text
              p.article__paragraph.text
                | Neither at school nor at the institute do they
                | teach us how to study the material correctly. We are
                | preparing for exams and learning tickets. We train
                | ourselves to solve repetitive problems in order
                | to pass the test better, but often in the end this does
                | not give us real knowledge. Cramming quickly disappears and
                | does not bring any benefit.
              p.article__paragraph.text
                span.article__span-accent Conclusion:
                | you also need to be able to learn, but for some
                | reason this is not taught anywhere. What
                | to do with it?
              p.article__paragraph.text
                | Specific techniques and exercises help to change the
                | approach to learning, make it effective and exciting.
                | The same techniques are applied on the example
                | of training in the Practicum.
